annot explain rebirth is due to inherent limitations in classical science. Modern science has transcended these limitations, and therefore rebirth is within the scope of modern science. Modern science accepts rebirth as a scientifically acceptable phenome
non through the same tests used to prove scientific acceptability of generally accepted modern science phenomena. 
